@startuml
title Sequence 07 - Mengajukan Surat Pengantar
autonumber
actor Mahasiswa
participant "Frontend Portal\nLaporan" as FE
participant "Document API\n/api/v1/document-requests" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Celery Worker" as Worker

Mahasiswa -> FE: Isi tipe dokumen dan tujuan surat
FE -> API: POST /document-requests
API -> DB: Cek request tipe sama dalam 5 menit terakhir
alt cooldown aman
  API -> DB: Insert DocumentRequests status=PENDING
  DB --> API: document_id
  API -> Worker: Queue generate_cover_letter(document_id)
  API --> FE: Request diterima
  FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan status PENDING/PROCESSING
else masih cooldown
  API --> FE: 429 Too Many Requests
  FE --> Mahasiswa: Tampilkan pesan tunggu
end
@enduml
